Title: Spring Collection
Description:
That maggot Ren'khat wants my position, hm? He's welcome to try and take it.

All the runoff from our operation flows into the spring below Rak-Ahat. Decades of mordants, catalysts, and alchemical concoctions have coalesced into something quite... potent.

Don't fuss about the side effects. Just bring me a good variety of dyestuffs and I'll brew up colors that will have you growing extra pairs of legs.
ObjectivesText: Collect 12 Reclaimed Catalyst, as well as 3 Luminous Strangler Sap, 3 Eyeless Petals, and 3 Cochineal Crawlers.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Grand Overspinner Antourix at the spinneret in Rak-Ahat.
RewardText: I think these will do. You're not as useless as I expected.
